headline: Here’s Why GreenWood Investors Decided to Sell Texas Pacific Land (TPL)
summary: GreenWood Investors, an investment management company, released its fourth quarter investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund’s separate accounts composite generated 16.6% returns, in 2024, roughly in line with the benchmark MSCI ACWI return of 16.3%.
